rows.label: bf04320100_0010

Professor Tatezo! Give us
proper instructions already!

guarantee safety your life, Professor.

rows.label: bf04320100_0030
rows.name:
Reduce the neural circuit
load by twenty percent.

rows.label: bf04320100_0040
rows.name:
That should improve
production efficiency.

rows.label: bf04320100_0050
rows.name:
You should have cooperated
from the start.

rows.label: bf04320100_0060
rows.name: Hey! Isn't that...

rows.name: [ML:undisp ]!

rows.name: Y-you are[ML:Dash ] Tora, is that you, Mo-mo?

rows.name: Dad Tatezo[ML:Dash ] is that you, Mo-mo?

rows.label: bf04320100_0110
rows.name: Tora!

rows.label: bf04320100_0120
rows.name: Dad!

rows.label: bf04320100_0130
rows.name: I missed you so much, mo!

rows.label: bf04320100_0140
rows.name: I missed you too, mo!

rows.name: Tora, I'm so glad.

rows.label: bf04320100_0160
rows.name: *sniff*

rows.name: And these people are[ML:Dash ]

I see, you've made[ML:Dash ] such

rows.label: bf04320100_0230
rows.name:
Mo mo... Most impressive.
Tora must have worked hard!

rows.label: bf04320100_0240
rows.name:
Everyone, I'm sure you have much to talk
about, but let's focus on escaping first.

rows.label: bf04320100_0250
rows.name: Ah, that's right. Hurry, Rex.

rows.label: bf04320100_0260
rows.name: Yeah.

rows.label: bf04320100_0290

Muimui give you information on
purpose, to lure you to factory.

rows.label: bf04320100_0320
rows.name:
If we not want you here, you would
never find this place so easily!

rows.label: bf04320100_0330
rows.name: You bastard[ML:Dash ] I won't forgive you, mo!

rows.label: bf04320100_0340
rows.name: Masterpon is really angry.

rows.label: bf04320100_0350

Mo... Finally I have chance to
seize precious artificial Blade.
